to stare at somebody like that.

107
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:20,050
But I am really

108
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:23,110
so cute that if I don't do that,

109
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:25,620
people will laugh at me.

110
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:35,130
But maybe you have seen him before.

111
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,670
I think my building is right ahead.

112
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:42,050
We also work around here.

113
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:44,380
Which building do you work in?

114
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:48,170
I still have time. I can send you there.

115
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,300
Oppa!

116
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,480
Really?

117
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:54,380
Thank you so much.

118
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:57,268
