in front of that building.

119
00:08:57,908 --> 00:08:58,308
What?

120
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,410
What a coincidence.

121
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:02,160
That's also where I'm going.

122
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:05,540
Kim Yeong, I'm afraid
you have to take some walk.

123
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:07,180
You get off here, OK?

124
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:09,790
