Don't worry.

207
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:42,960
The US?

208
00:16:43,380 --> 00:16:43,680
Yes.

209
00:16:44,628 --> 00:16:45,977
He was originally in the US branch,

210
00:16:46,297 --> 00:16:48,030
until he was transferred here to be

211
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:49,030
our general manager.

212
00:16:50,340 --> 00:16:54,820
Our branch's sales last year
was not very good,

213
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:58,420
