together with him this morning?

220
00:17:24,740 --> 00:17:28,060
I didn't want to be late,
so I tried to take a cab.

221
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,691
But nothing turned out right.

222
00:17:29,851 --> 00:17:31,140
But nothing turned out right.

223
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:32,960
In the end, Lee Jun

224
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:33,565
