225
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:35,702
Yes.

226
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:44,350
I'll make another cup.
Please take mine.

227
00:17:44,388 --> 00:17:45,188
Thank you, Group Leader.

228
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,640
- Lee Jun?
- Yes.

229
00:17:52,502 --> 00:17:53,200
