233
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,890
How did your talk go?

234
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,410
Lee Jun is the last one.

235
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:27,000
I'm still scared, come to think of it.

236
00:18:27,580 --> 00:18:28,891
