the general manager this morning.

253
00:19:13,940 --> 00:19:15,520
Could he be...

254
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:20,660
Jun, that's pretty fast.

255
00:19:21,508 --> 00:19:21,771
Yes.

256
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:23,550
String-puller?

257
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:27,300
I think we are all string-pullers.

258
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:31,310
After all, we all came
through special recruitment.

259
00:19:33,074 --> 00:19:33,645
Didn't we?

260
00:19:36,045 --> 00:19:36,731
Thank you.

261
00:19:49,390 --> 00:19:57,005
