00:20:28,251 --> 00:20:30,651
You saved me. I won't forget that.

269
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:37,700
Your resumé is really one of a kind.

270
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:42,720
What's on it is novel and fun.

271
00:20:46,045 --> 00:20:46,742
Manager in a cafe.

272
00:20:48,422 --> 00:20:49,702
Is cat cafe a real stuff?

273
00:20:50,365 --> 00:20:50,720
Yes.

274
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:55,140
You can feed
and take care of cats there.

275
00:20:57,131 --> 00:20:57,817
That sounds fun.

276
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:15,600
I'm interested in those
fragrance-themed products.

277
00:21:17,462 --> 00:21:22,220
Can you be specific about this?

278
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:30,070
Whenever something important
happens to me

279
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:32,280
or I feel tired,

280
00:21:33,140 --> 00:21:36,350
someone always gives me advice
with fragrances.

281
00:21:37,540 --> 00:21:38,520
So when I learned that

282
00:21:38,580 --> 00:21:41,840
we have fragrance-themed products,
I became interested.

283
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:49,480
Who is that person?

284
00:22:01,805 --> 00:22:03,177
Is it Group Leader Song Hyun-jae?

285
00:22:03,851 --> 00:22:04,708
Yes.

286
00:22:06,651 --> 00:22:09,660
Your letter of recommendation
was written by him.

287
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,770
Looks like he helped you a lot.

288
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:14,260
He did.

289
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:18,250
Hyun-jae, I mean, Group Leader,

290
00:22:18,660 --> 00:22:20,022
is a person
whom I should thank a lot.

291
00:22:21,428 --> 00:22:21,954
I see.

292
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:28,845
Jun, can I ask you a question?

293
00:22:30,342 --> 00:22:30,708
Sure.

294
00:22:37,417 --> 00:22:51,370
From this time to this time,
how was your life?

295
00:23:20,580 --> 00:23:23,337
♪I miss you so much♪

296
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:29,497
It's been a long time.
How have you been?

297
00:23:30,114 --> 00:23:34,720
♪I have been waiting for you♪

298
00:23:35,234 --> 00:23:37,980
♪I'm trying so hard to forget you♪

299
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:38,331
Choi Jun?

300
00:23:39,497 --> 00:23:40,274
Choi Jun.

301
00:23:41,580 --> 00:23:43,340
Remember what I told you?

302
00:23:43,340 --> 00:23:45,931
You should run or win the fight.

303
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:48,950
Do you want to be bullied every day?

304
00:23:49,474 --> 00:23:51,577
I knew you would come to help me.

305
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:55,890
What if I didn't come?

306
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:59,200
I can't be by your side every day.

307
00:23:59,977 --> 00:24:00,308
Why not?

308
00:24:02,777 --> 00:24:03,337
What why not?

309
00:24:03,954 --> 00:24:06,102
Didn't you say
you'd be with me forever?

310
00:24:07,142 --> 00:24:10,274
Oh, I did say that.

311
00:24:11,611 --> 00:24:13,020
But what happened today...

312
00:24:14,260 --> 00:24:16,270
- Thank you, Lee Jun.
- Huh?

313
00:24:17,988 --> 00:24:18,560
Thank you.

314
00:24:26,582 --> 00:24:28,080
You smell so nice.

315
00:24:30,925 --> 00:24:31,965
I have a smell on me?

316
00:24:32,628 --> 00:24:34,160
Yes, fragrance.

317
00:24:35,405 --> 00:24:36,937
Fragrance?

318
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:47,560
(Choi Jun is always with a fragrance,)

319
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:50,022
(a soft and warm one.)

320
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:13,120
(Jun and Jun)

321
00:25:13,130 --> 00:25:16,262
The primary sales planning work

322
00:25:16,491 --> 00:25:18,171
will be on you guys.

323
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:21,828
(That means this position
doesn't belong to me yet.)

324
00:25:22,742 --> 00:25:26,810
(Classic rookie,
making rookie mistakes.)

325
00:25:26,891 --> 00:25:28,742
(Sorry for the trouble
I keep bringing you.)

326
00:25:29,108 --> 00:25:30,400
(I actually like it.)

327
00:25:30,754 --> 00:25:32,068
(It's a special hobby.)

328
00:25:32,582 --> 00:25:35,800
(I want to return all the things
I got from you.)
